snippet.title: Strangeland launch trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Windows on May 25th, 2021!
Wishlist on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1369520/Strangeland/

You wake in a surreal carnival, where a woman cries out to you before leaping to her death. Who was she? And who are you? The denizens and devices of Strangeland answer with riddles, puzzles, and warnings of a Dark Thing lurking at the park’s peak. A new adventure from the creators of Primordia.

Developed by: Wormwood Studios
Published by: Wadjet Eye Games
Trailer voiceover: Abe Goldfarb, Lucas Schuneman, Mike Ciporkin, Maya Murphy, Mike Pollock, Abby Wahl, Steven Kelly
Trailer music: Victor Pflug
Trailer editing: Alasdair Beckett-King
